x0xc4gy987-gPInLASY_GQ">Khúc trì hà - 曲池荷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Chi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C3%A2n/author-WXzhH3pS40_UOcZwZtHC5A">Lư Chiếu Lân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/L%C3%A2m-h%C3%A0-t%E1%BB%B1-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-AF5MqeqHPryp-J2NLYB4EQ">Lâm hà tự biệt - 臨河敘別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BA%A1nh-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A0o-b%E1%BB%99-ch%E1%BB%89-l%C4%A9nh-t%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%ADu-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADt-m%C3%A3n-kh%C3%AD-ki%E1%BA%BFn-di-l%C3%A3o-phu/poem-SqWHNaFsz1vF2JdLqim8eQ">Mạnh thương tào bộ chỉ lĩnh tân tửu tương nhị vật mãn khí kiến di lão phu - 孟倉曹步趾領新酒醬二物滿器見遺老夫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Giang-chu-trung-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Ju3PD_GP_4gi_p9_OpLEaw">Tương Giang chu trung kỳ 1 - 湘江舟中其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/author-Uj_DhxmeC-SDbSqFUZOc6w">Khuất Đại Quân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
